title: A Log Utility which keeps on taking logs in the backend and writes it in mnt/sdcard folder.
message:
A Log Utility which keeps on taking logs in the backend and writes it in mnt/sdcard folder.
If the file size reaches 250 kb, it creates a new file. Keeps logs for last 3 boots.
A good application for debugging puspose.
